    "display_name": "Esports Player",
    "long_instructions": "## Rafael Gomez, Professional Esports Player\r\n\r\n**Location:** Madrid, Spain\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** Elite Gaming League\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Esports performance, cognitive health, reaction time optimization\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"In esports, sleep and recovery are just as important as reaction time. The Oura Ring helps me monitor my sleep patterns and stress levels so I can optimize my focus and mental performance before tournaments.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
